Marcel Mouloudji https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcel_Mouloudji 0 Marcel André Mouloudji (16 September 1922 – 14 June 1994) was a French singer and actor who was born in Paris and died in Neuilly-sur-Seine. He sang songs written by Boris Vian and Jacques Prévert.
